>\n研究：飲水令到頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哈<br />\n你今日咗飲水?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14W60G0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14W60G0.jpg&h=7b561bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n百份之99.9999999999%嘅人死之前嗰日都有飲過水</blockquote><br />\n淨返果d 係咪未出世/一出世就死</blockquote><br />\n飲左羊水"},{"pid":"f407af7cc06ae9502183efce11aa2109c26c575b","tid":219344,"uid":200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:09:37.000Z","msg":"我屌你表姐啊"},{"pid":"2ff2f65ec94251710bc4860358cfe95da337fea6","tid":219344,"uid":64008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:10:19.000Z","msg":"點證明表兄弟姊妹通婚同有無APOC3有直接關係？"},{"pid":"f05e114d46326b9d96da676421be409cca379b15","tid":219344,"uid":93712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:26:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>香港表親結婚唔係亂倫</blockquote><br />\n李嘉誠就係同表妹結婚</blockquote><br />\n表得 堂唔得</blockquote><br />\n堂親都係得<br />\n<br />\n見第181章《婚姻條例》附表5<br />\n<br />\n另見第200章《刑事罪行條例》47-48條：<br />\n<br />\n任何男子與一名女子性交而知道該女子是他的孫女、外孫女、女、姐妹或母親，即屬犯罪，一經循公訴程序定罪，可處監禁14年<br />\n<br />\n任何年齡在16歲或以上的女子，同意而准許她的祖父、外祖父、父親、兄弟或兒子與她性交(而知道該人是她的祖父、外祖父、父親、兄弟或兒子(視屬何情況而定))，即屬犯罪，一經循公訴程序定罪，可處監禁14年。"},{"pid":"ea9c03fdea1f32e7d9712f52ee5d315f0ecf809f","tid":219344,"uid":3716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:26:58.000Z","msg":"不了<br />\n堂姐妹太7"},{"pid":"6e1e0ea63426dc166624750cc1ad310728cc4dfa","tid":219344,"uid":32006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:28:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>廢話<br />\n<br />\n利申 :  同表姐扑過, 但係心肺功能一直都好廢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪後代先得?"},{"pid":"413d1825834e3c59d77a814b28d3bd7b2bc6bef3","tid":219344,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:28:42.000Z","