" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國傳統唔多介意姨表、姑表結婚，<br />\n但好似唔多接受堂兄妹結婚(雖則遺傳距離上同前兩者無分別)</blockquote><br />\n唔好嚇我喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前啲戲除左話其實你地係兄妹所以唔結得婚之外<br />\n連同姓都唔比架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n堂兄妹咪同姓囉 做咩姐你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"485a2502012ed86ab1575fef47c21ed2a02ba202","tid":219344,"uid":80311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:14:26.000Z","msg":"<del>與堂表兄弟姐妹</del>做愛 能抗心臟病"},{"pid":"3b1dc2986c2ba92d3446ab8629817112296d9066","tid":219344,"uid":89441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:19:23.000Z","msg":"巴基斯坦既研究就...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b03cf41b85c86c2062e310fc3c7a85dbddffda","tid":219344,"uid":20835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然說與堂表兄弟姊妹結婚或做愛，在現代是極具爭議的話題，甚至有國家法律禁止通婚，以防基因太近而讓下一代出現疾病。但巴基斯坦一項最新研究發現，與堂表兄弟姊妹做愛，可以降低罹患心臟病的機會。<br />\n據英國《每日星報》報導，這份研究針對巴基斯坦一個靠海邊的小漁村進行，科學家對當地村民進行研究，因為這裡的村民流行表兄弟姊妹通婚。研究後發現，這裡有超過1800位居民，都沒有「APOC3」基因，這個基因會控制新陳代謝與脂蛋白，而這與心臟病有所關聯。科學家也指出，這些少了「APOC3」基因的村民，就不會經歷像一般人吃了高熱量食物後，會產生血漿甘油三酸酯的狀況，三酸甘油酯的程度也不高，這也意味著這些村民罹患心臟疾病的風險較低。<br />\n研究人員沙辛(Danish Saleheen)就指出，這份報告是首度證實APOC3基因對人體健康的重要性。而他也表示，這個漁村的村民透過近親通婚，讓他們「洗掉」APOC3基因，也讓這裡的居民罹患心臟疾病的狀況不多。（<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">施旖婕</span></span>／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/recommend/20170427/1106329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Frecommend%2F20170427%2F1106329&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=732c7fb1\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/recommend/20170427/1106329</a><br />\n<br />\n鼓勵亂倫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6046f711d8284be614f9cf02da75025a79b960","tid":219344,"uid":4326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:32:22.000Z","msg":"堂兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6ad2bc35e5cfb54d3229fff2941cba4c9b2a95","tid":219344,"uid":35199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:32:25.000Z","msg":"禁止亂倫一定係各國政府陰謀，怕人類覺醒。"},{"pid":"0ff2ad8e68d439d6682cbf79ac8528fa579b2f86","tid":219344,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T11:40:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中國人不嬲唔介意，只會當親上加親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果堂表兄弟姊妹搞男女關係係「亂倫」嘅，咁成本紅樓夢就係亂倫大作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國傳統唔多介意姨表、姑表結婚，<br />\n但好似唔多接受堂兄妹結婚(雖則遺傳距離上同前兩者無分別)</blockquote><br />\n唔好嚇我喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前啲戲除左話其實你地係兄妹所以唔結得婚之外<br />\n連同姓都唔比架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n堂兄妹咪同